'''超融合基礎架構'''（{{lang|en|Hyper-converged infrastructure}}，縮寫爲HCI），是一種整合了[[電腦數據存貯器|儲存設備]]及[[虛擬化|虛擬運算]]的資訊基礎架構框架。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/05/04/hyperconvergence_hype_de_hyped/ | title=Hyper-convergence? I believe – just not like this | website=The Register | date=2015-05-04 | accessdate=2016-09-20 | author=Trevor Pott | archive-date=2016-09-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160906151301/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/05/04/hyperconvergence_hype_de_hyped | dead-url=no }}</ref>在這樣的架構環境中，同一廠商的伺服器與儲存等硬體單元，搭配虛擬化軟體，被整合在一個[[机箱|機箱]]之中。<ref>{{cite book | title=The Gorilla Guide to Hyperconverged Infrastructure Implementation Strategies | publisher=ActualTech Marketing | author=Scott Lowe | year=2015 | isbn=1943952000}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | title=Hyperconvergence Fundamentals and the Maxta Advantage | publisher=ActualTech Marketing | author=David Davis, Scott Lowe | year=2015 | isbn=1943952019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bizjournals.com/boston/blog/startups/2015/12/guest-commentary-the-next-big-tech-trend-in-2016.html | title=Guest commentary: The next big tech trend in 2016? Hyperconvergence | website=Bizjournals | date=2015-12-23 | accessdate=2016-09-20 | author=Maia Heymann}}</ref>這個名詞是從「{{le|融合基礎架構|Converged infrastructure}}」衍生而成而成的[[新词|新词]]，意爲可提供比融合式架構更進一步的「融合」<ref name="ithome102114">{{cite web | url=http://www.ithome.com.tw/tech/102114 | title=什麼是超融合架構？ | website=iThome | date=2016-01-03 | accessdate=2016-09-20 | author=張明德 | archive-date=2016-09-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915232625/http://www.ithome.com.tw/tech/102114 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://searchstorage.techtarget.com/magazineContent/Convergence-reaches-a-new-level|title=Convergence reaches a new level|author=Arun Taneja|access-date=March 4, 2016|website=TechTarget|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927115059/http://searchstorage.techtarget.com/magazineContent/Convergence-reaches-a-new-level|archive-date=2016-09-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
==特色==
概括來說，超融合基礎架構能提供[[資料中心|資料中心]]在可用性及可靠性上的需要，而且整個系統能被集中管理，所有對設備硬體的管理工作均可透過單一軟體界面完成。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nutanix.com/2016/02/01/the-tesla-effect-how-hyperconvergence-solves-enterprise-storage-challenges/|title=The Tesla Effect – How Hyperconvergence Solves Enterprise Storage Challenges|accessdate=2016-09-20|author=Steve Kaplan|date=2016-02-01|website=Nutanix|language=|archive-date=2016-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160912230937/http://www.nutanix.com/2016/02/01/the-tesla-effect-how-hyperconvergence-solves-enterprise-storage-challenges/|dead-url=no}}</ref>與融合式架構的差別在於，融合式架構是以套件爲單位，其硬體架構是分散的，伺服器與儲存設備是各自獨立的；超融合基礎架構則是將[[伺服器|伺服器]]與儲存整合在一個單元機箱爲來提供服務。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eweek.com/enterprise-apps/hds-pentaho-join-for-hyper-converged-data-center-system.html|title=HDS, Pentaho Join for Hyper-Converged Data Center System|accessdate=2016-02-08|author=Chris Preimesberger|date=2016-02-05|website=eWeek}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/07/03/super_mega_hyperconvergence/ | title=It's not for everyone, but hyperconvergence is still a valuable solution | website=The Register | date=2015-07-03 | accessdate=2016-09-20 | author=Enrico Signoretti | archive-date=2016-12-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229145337/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/07/03/super_mega_hyperconvergence/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>換言之，在超融合基礎架構中，不需要專用的存儲子系統（如磁碟陣列）。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://enterprise.huawei.com/topic/servers/FusionCube/technology3.html | title=超越融合：超融合架构相关概念与分类 | website=华为技术有限公司 | accessdate=2016-09-20 | archive-date=2016-09-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160902032209/http://enterprise.huawei.com/topic/servers/FusionCube/technology3.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

超融合基礎架構跳脫了一個只是打包在一起的系統，而是進化成一個運行在現成[[x86|x86]]伺服器上的軟體定義運行環境。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stratoscale.com/blog/industry-buzz/the-private-cloud-a-balancing-act/|title=The Private Cloud. A Balancing Act|accessdate=2016-09-20|author=Benoit Hudzia|date=2015-04-08|website=Stratoscale|archive-date=2016-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161003233115/http://www.stratoscale.com/blog/industry-buzz/the-private-cloud-a-balancing-act/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.datacenterknowledge.com/archives/2015/12/10/why-hyperconverged-infrastructure-is-so-hot/|title=Why Hyperconverged Infrastructure is so Hot|accessdate=2016-09-20|author=Yevgeniy Sverdlik|date=2015-12-10|website=Data Center Knowledge|archive-date=2016-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160909125742/http://www.datacenterknowledge.com/archives/2015/12/10/why-hyperconverged-infrastructure-is-so-hot/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://virtualizationreview.com/articles/2015/08/28/hyperconvergence-hype-and-promise.aspx|title=Hyperconvergence: Hype and Promise|accessdate=2016-09-20|author=Jon William Toigo|date=2015-08-28|work=|website=Virtualization Review|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424063656/https://virtualizationreview.com/articles/2015/08/28/hyperconvergence-hype-and-promise.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>它的架構由一致的安裝了本地儲存裝置的x86伺服器所組成，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.networkworld.com/article/3020668/virtualization/containers-hyperconvergence-and-disaggregation-are-hot.html|title=Containers, hyperconvergence and disaggregation are hot|accessdate=2016-09-20|author=Jim Duffy|date=2016-01-11|website=Network World|archive-date=2016-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160905140503/http://www.networkworld.com/article/3020668/virtualization/containers-hyperconvergence-and-disaggregation-are-hot.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.itworldcanada.com/article/stratoscale-expands-hyperconvergence-market-with-symphony/379299 | title=Stratoscale expands hyperconvergence market | website=IT World Canada | date=2015-12-14 | accessdate=2016-09-20 | author=Danny Bradbury | archive-date=2016-08-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160802210029/http://www.itworldcanada.com/article/stratoscale-expands-hyperconvergence-market-with-symphony/379299 | dead-url=no }}</ref>所有資源的調派均不涉及底層實體硬體的組態設定，而是以虛擬機爲核心，以單一的{{Link-en|軟體定義資料中心|Software-defined data center|軟體定義方式}}來規畫底層硬體，然後向用戶交付需要的資源，因而具備了管理簡單、類似積木堆疊方式彈性擴充等特性；而藉由叢集架構還可容忍部份節點故障，並迅速地調整配置，讓資訊中心能更有效率並且降低總體擁有成本。<ref name="ithome102114"></ref><ref name="ithome92534">{{cite web | url=http://www.ithome.com.tw/tech/92534 | title=超融合架構解構傳統IT機房 | website=iThome | date=2014-11-27 | accessdate=2016-09-20 | author=張明德 | archive-date=2016-08-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822024302/http://www.ithome.com.tw/tech/92534 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://searchitchannel.techtarget.com/feature/Selling-hyper-converged-architecture-A-channel-primer | title=Selling hyper-converged architecture: A channel primer | website=TechTarget | accessdate=2016-09-20 | author=John Moore | archive-date=2016-09-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919004918/http://searchitchannel.techtarget.com/feature/Selling-hyper-converged-architecture-A-channel-primer | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.crn.com/news/storage/300074674/cisco-intel-invest-in-hyper-converged-infrastructure-player-stratoscale.htm | title=Cisco, Intel Invest In Hyper-Converged Infrastructure Player Stratoscale | website=The Channel Company | date=2014-11-04 | accessdate=2016-09-20 | author=Joseph F. Kovar | archive-date=2016-08-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823013029/http://www.crn.com/news/storage/300074674/cisco-intel-invest-in-hyper-converged-infrastructure-player-stratoscale.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://wikibon.org/wiki/v/Converged_Infrastructure_Moves_from_Infant_to_Adolescent | title=Converged Infrastructure Moves from Infant to Adolescent | website=Wikibon | date=2012-12-10 | accessdate=2016-09-20 | author=David Vellante | archive-date=2016-08-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819130854/http://wikibon.org/wiki/v/Converged_Infrastructure_Moves_from_Infant_to_Adolescent | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/adrianbridgwater/2015/06/10/nutanix-why-cloud-was-never-really-flexible-until-hyperconvergence/#2715e4857a0b6333321567ab | title=Nutanix: Why Cloud Was Never Really Flexible, Until Hyperconvergence | website=Forbes | date=2015-06-10 | accessdate=2016-09-20 | author=Adrian Bridgwater | archive-date=2016-09-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160913021315/http://www.forbes.com/sites/adrianbridgwater/2015/06/10/nutanix-why-cloud-was-never-really-flexible-until-hyperconvergence/#2715e4857a0b6333321567ab | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==可能的影響==
超融合基礎架構使得企業無需再面對各種不同廠牌的伺服器及儲存系統，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://searchnetworking.techtarget.com/tip/Hyper-converged-infrastructure-forcing-new-thinking-for-networks|title=Hyper-converged infrastructure forcing new thinking for networks|accessdate=2016-09-20|author=Patrick Hubbard|date=|website=Techtarget|archive-date=2016-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160929053114/http://searchnetworking.techtarget.com/tip/Hyper-converged-infrastructure-forcing-new-thinking-for-networks|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然它目前在市場上仍然無法替代儲存系統，但是它將促進簡化系統管理工作以及提高資源利用率。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.itbusinessedge.com/blogs/infrastructure/it-turns-to-hyperconvergence-but-is-it-right-for-all-occasions.html|title=IT Turns to Hyperconvergence, But Is It Right for All Occasions?|accessdate=2016-09-20|author=Arthur Cole|date=2015-11-04|website=IT Business Edge|archive-date=2016-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807142452/http://www.itbusinessedge.com/blogs/infrastructure/it-turns-to-hyperconvergence-but-is-it-right-for-all-occasions.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.information-age.com/it-management/strategy-and-innovation/123460680/why-hyperconvergence-and-robots-are-cios-innovation-starting-blocks|title=Why hyperconvergence and robots are the CIO's innovation starting blocks|accessdate=2016-09-20|author=Chloe Green|date=2015-12-14|website=Information Age|archive-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826124714/http://www.information-age.com/it-management/strategy-and-innovation/123460680/why-hyperconvergence-and-robots-are-cios-innovation-starting-blocks|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eweek.com/storage/slideshows/ibm-sees-flash-hyper-convergence-among-top-2016-storage-trends.html|title=IBM Sees Flash, Hyper-convergence Among Top 2016 Storage Trends|accessdate=2016-09-20|author=Darryl K. Taft|date=2016-01-04|website=eWeek}}</ref>

[[高德纳咨询公司|高德纳公司]]預計，超融合基礎架構市場規模將從2016年的近20億美元增長到2019年的約50億美元，在融合系統市場占比達24%，並在2020年成為資料中心的主流。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gartner.com/newsroom/id/3308017 | title=Gartner Says Hyperconverged Integrated Systems Will Be Mainstream in Five Years | publisher=Gartner | date=2016-05-05 | accessdate=2016-09-20 | archive-date=2016-09-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160925080020/http://www.gartner.com/newsroom/id/3308017 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

